articles.title: Photos: Spain win first Women’s World Cup, beating England 1-0 - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: Spain become the first European team to win the Women’s World Cup since Germany in 2007.
articles.content:
Spain has won their first Womens World Cup title less than a year after a player rebellion, holding off England 1-0 on Sunday after Olga Carmonas first-half goal.
